<h1>About</h1>

<p>Toronto is a dynamic city full of vibrant neighbourhoods each with their own distinctive boutiques, markets and cafes. Shop the Block makes it easy and cost-effective for shoppers like you, who favour quality and friendly service, to support your favourite independent merchants.</p>
<h4>Shop the Block Benefits</h4>
<p>The Shop the Block discount card gives you preferred savings on the goods and services you buy for yourself and your family at dozens of unique stores and restaurants in your neighbourhood and around the GTA.</p>
<p>Why Shop the Block?</p>
<ul>
  <li>To save money at your favourite stores and local businesses</li>
  <li>To help you get more for less</li>
  <li>To make shopping convenient and enjoyable</li>
  <li>To provide you with the freedom to shop where you want </li>
  <li> To be able to buy everything from the exclusive to the accessible at competitive pricing, all in one place</li>
  <li>To support independent neighbourhood merchants</li>
  <li>To stay involved with your community</li>
</ul>
